title: Ep. 432 - Real Journalists Expose Fake News
description:
CNN chief Jeff Zucker gets caught on camera telling his “journalists” to push impeachment, and the mainstream media lose their minds over a meme. Then Beto adds honesty to our discourse, and Kanye West adds family values. Finally, a preview of tonight’s debate. Date: 10-15-2019
